.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: fuchsia, aquamarine, pink, purple, mauve
Nationality: malaysian, italian, mexican, colombian, german
Cigar: ritmeester, oliveros, davidoff, bongani, alhambra
Beverage: fanta, sprite, hot-chocolate, juice, 7up
Pet: fish, snake, ferret, bird, lizard

1. Nationality:malaysian == Color:fuchsia
2. Nationality:italian == Pet:fish
3. Beverage:fanta == Color:aquamarine
4. Nationality:mexican == Beverage:sprite
5. Color:aquamarine is to the right of Color:pink
6. Cigar:ritmeester == Pet:lizard
7. Cigar:oliveros == Color:purple
8. Beverage:hot-chocolate is in the middle
9. Nationality:colombian is on the far left
10. Cigar:davidoff is on the left or right of Pet:snake
11. Cigar:oliveros is to the left or right of Pet:bird
12. Cigar:bongani == Beverage:juice
13. Nationality:german == Cigar:alhambra
14. Nationality:colombian is to the left or right of Color:mauve

